snippet.title: Capcom Arcade Cabinet (XBLA) - Full Gameplay Tour
snippet.description:
Captured off the Xbox One. Despite the free-to-play Capcom Arcade Stadium and 2nd Stadium being available on Xbox One and PS4, the M2-developed Arcade Cabinet (released in 2013 for Capcom's 30th Anniversary) for the Xbox 360 is backward compatible on Xbox One and Series X|S.
